    "Current data plane elements (routers, switches etc.)",
    "are equipped with more powerful storage and computing techniques able to gather richer data monitoring view of the network [9].",
    "These conditions ease and ameliorate learning about the network to better supervise it.The purpose of this paper is to discuss the benefits and limitation of applying such techniques in the NFV ecosystem by surveying existing approaches.",
    "The objective is to alert the research community to the potential role that ML could play in resolving problems related to NFV.",
    "Note that many good surveys have already investigated the ML applications to different domains linked to NFV like the Cloud Computing in [10][11][12][13][14], the SDN [15], the Big data in [16,17] the Internet of Things in [18,19] and for networking in general [20]."
